  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654820/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1763397224\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654820/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1763397224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/654820/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1763397224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Once again, you only have to draw one continuous line. <br><br>When you draw on a tile, it will change color from orange to blue or from blue to orange. You solve each puzzle, by making all tiles akin. <br><br>There are 96 puzzles on \"Normal\"-mode and 96 puzzles in \"Time\"-mode. Each puzzles can have many different solutions. Start with basic puzzles and unlock harder ones. <br><br>There are also special tiles. The \"Teleport\"-tile, teleports the line to another point in the puzzle. The \"Double Use\"-tile can be used twice, which is requires to solve some of the puzzles",
  "about_the_game": "Once again, you only have to draw one continuous line. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhen you draw on a tile, it will change color from orange to blue or from blue to orange. You solve each puzzle, by making all tiles akin. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are 96 puzzles on \"Normal\"-mode and 96 puzzles in \"Time\"-mode. Each puzzles can have many different solutions. Start with basic puzzles and unlock harder ones. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are also special tiles. The \"Teleport\"-tile, teleports the line to another point in the puzzle. The \"Double Use\"-tile can be used twice, which is requires to solve some of the puzzles",
